---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Returns & Exchanges" description="Our hassle-free 30-day return policy.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-(--font-heading) text-4xl text-(--color-text-base) mb-3">Returns & Exchanges</h1>
      <p class="text-(--color-text-muted) text-sm max-w-lg mx-auto">
        We want you to love your purchase. If something is not right, we are here to help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-(--color-surface) border border-(--color-border) rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] p-8">
        <h2 class="font-(--font-heading) text-2xl text-(--color-text-base) mb-3">30-Day Return Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
          You may return most items within 30 days of delivery for a full refund or exchange.
          To be eligible, items must be unused, in the same condition as received, and in the
          original packaging with all tags attached.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-surface) border border-(--color-border) rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] p-8">
        <h2 class="font-(--font-heading) text-2xl text-(--color-text-base) mb-3">How to Start a Return</h2>
        <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-(--color-text-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-2">
          <li>Contact our support team via email with your order number and reason for return.</li>
          <li>We will provide a prepaid return shipping label within 24 hours.</li>
          <li>Pack the item securely in its original packaging, including all accessories and tags.</li>
          <li>Drop the package at the nearest shipping carrier location.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-surface) border border-(--color-border) rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] p-8">
        <h2 class="font-(--font-heading) text-2xl text-(--color-text-base) mb-3">Refunds</h2>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Once we receive and inspect your return, we will notify you of the approval status.
          Approved refunds will be processed to the original payment method within 5–7 business days.
          You will receive an email confirmation once the refund has been issued.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-surface) border border-(--color-border) rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] p-8">
        <h2 class="font-(--font-heading) text-2xl text-(--color-text-base) mb-3">Exchanges</h2>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
          If you need a different size, color, or item, the fastest way is to return the original
          order and place a new order separately. This ensures the quickest processing and
          availability of stock.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-(--color-surface) border border-(--color-border) rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] p-8">
        <h2 class="font-(--font-heading) text-2xl text-(--color-text-base) mb-3">Non-Returnable Items</h2>
        <p class="text-(--color-text-muted) text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Certain items are not eligible for return, including final sale items, intimate apparel,
          and gift cards. Please check the product page for any specific return restrictions before
          purchasing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
